race.comment: VALUBIOUS (11) is unlucky to still be a maiden finishing runner-up at the past couple and strikes a very winnable contest here. Maps ideally for this from gate three and looks the one they all have to run down. CHANCE (2) has hit the top-five in all seven starts to date and seems to be on the doorstep of a maiden victory. Well placed to break the ice. RED CITY SUN (4) will be ready to peak now fourth run back and gets the services of Wiggins in the irons. Top-three aspirations. SECRET SCOUT (5) should be rock-hard fit for this and may earn some minor money. SHE'S A SWEET STAR (10) best of the rest from the inside marble.
